---
title: Pesto Stuffed Chicken with sweet potato mash and chorizo broccoli
description: Perfectly tender broccoli florets are always a treat for the senses, but in this recipe, they're kicked up a notch with a chorizo and hazelnut crumb. The perfect pairing for cheesy pesto stuffed chicken and creamy sweet potato mash.
